      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog performance featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies to a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed: the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in and chassis balance these cars are known for. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic wear typical of a driven classic, the powertrain remains vigorous with consistent compression across all cylinders. It is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle optimized for performance rather than preservation.",
